  <brief_title>Respiratory Mechanics and Pleural Effusion</brief_title>
  <official_title>Estimation of Respiratory Mechanics (Respiratory System, Chest Wall and Lung Elastance) and Pleural Effusion at the Bedside With CT Scan.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
